These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
Flower: amaryllis, sunflower, azalea
1. Flower:azalea is on the far left or far right##3
2. Flower:sunflower is on the left of Flower:azalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Flower   | amaryllis | sunflower | azalea |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
Color: turquise, amber, blood-red
1. Color:amber is on the far left or far right##3
2. Color:blood-red is in the middle##1
3. Color:blood-red is on the right of Color:turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Color   | turquise | blood-red | amber |

 #################################
 
